{"tid":125852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有歌 怎敢說心事","createTime":"2017-02-19T00:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T03:42:32.000Z","uid":33880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c92d3f66a610cc0d6bb00226bbd882d7206ef48","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:25:05.000Z","msg":"受了傷 怎竟怕別人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n誰不捨我難過 分一丁目贈我<br />\n<br />\n不知道 不明瞭 不想要 為甚麼<br />\n<br />\n我不過是個人 都會難堪 <br />\n<br />\n你快樂過生活 我拼命去生存<br />\n幾多人位於山之巔俯瞰我的疲倦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊用歌詞放低你嘅心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d72174cb87cce80e611146ec8cf58d71a2f1a01","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"0df68f9368d1edf2fb7a4c08e681b4e08066037d","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好久不見 你還好嗎</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f84783ada46239e6e721937880b11e4bb4b8668a","tid":125852,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:31:57.000Z","msg":"越渴望見面然後發現<br />\n中間隔著那十年<br />\n我想見的笑臉<br />\n只有懷念<br />\n不懂怎去再聊天"},{"pid":"40b326d3eb26e1dbfe469774765854aba59c20e5","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>越渴望見面然後發現<br />\n中間隔著那十年<br />\n我想見的笑臉<br />\n只有懷念<br />\n不懂怎去再聊天</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如不見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c8ffb476f704b56830e3feb310e9d0d1d9ed09","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:35:56.000Z","msg":"連伴侶也要花費多幾倍力才望個夠<br />\n但仍然難擁有"},{"pid":"75d73a7ad91aa618f027320b1b9d2368d0d15f1c","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T00:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b75412bb26705669d5b28f4668432f4b85dc88c","tid":125852,"uid":68185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"金剛跟美女戀上 也是個傳奇狂想"},{"pid":"c361872b33e253476695ec5753fba3b41864dacc","tid":125852,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金剛跟美女戀上 也是個傳奇狂想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人人親近我 無人傾慕我"},{"pid":"0cd078d16e1b850ca698fa1fa68e34236b1b36f4","tid":125852,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"碌鳩已漸痕...銀行提現金"},{"pid":"a0d45f432b7787e1877414a58baf1a4b92b56351","tid":125852,"uid":29224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"我一早清楚<br />\n記憶始終會泛黃<br />\n為何在今夜<br />\n我放心把懷念釋放<br />\n幻化於空氣 飄過鬧市親親你<br />\n未怕你善忘 或已淡忘<br />\n<br />\n沒有誰負了誰<br />\n讓我放下了一切向異國飛去<br />\n仍沒有人能像你只需要一句<br />\n讓我帶笑改機票歸家去<br />\n<br />\n沒有誰負了誰<br />\n有些愛再努力最後總失去<br />\n明日上路 人沒法再掉傻眼淚<br />\n讓我將紙鶴安放掌心裏<br />\n<br />\n願那紙鶴掛在你心裏"}]}